ttm:role="x-roman">Sono hitotsubu wa</span></p><p begin="3:38.960" end="3:43.850" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:38.960" end="3:39.490">僕</span><span begin="3:39.490" end="3:40.160">の</span><span begin="3:40.720" end="3:41.400">中</span><span begin="3:41.400" end="3:41.580">に</span><span begin="3:41.580" end="3:42.100">あ</span><span begin="3:42.100" end="3:42.240">る</span><span begin="3:42.240" end="3:42.770">は</span><span begin="3:42.770" end="3:42.990">ず</span><span begin="3:42.990" end="3:43.510">な</span><span begin="3:43.510" end="3:43.690">の</span><span begin="3:43.690" end="3:43.850">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">明明理应存在于我的心中啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">明明理應存在於我的心中啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Should be inside me but</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 안에 있을 텐데</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Devrait pourtant être à l&apos;intérieur de moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque debería estar dentro de mí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sollte doch eigentlich in mir sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deveria estar dentro de mim apesar disso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Должна быть внутри меня но</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dovrebbe essere dentro di me eppure</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku no naka ni aru hazu na no ni</span></p><p begin="3:55.860" end="3:58.410" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:55.860" end="3:56.270">声</span><span begin="3:56.270" end="3:56.710">も</span><span begin="3:56.710" end="3:57.620">形</span><span begin="3:57.620" end="3:58.410">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论声音还是轮廓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論聲音還是輪廓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Both voice and shape</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">목소리도 형태도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si la voix et la forme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tanto la voz como la forma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sowohl Stimme als auch Gestalt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A voz e a forma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И голос и форма</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sia la voce che la forma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koe mo katachi mo</span></p><p begin="3:58.490" end="4:01.150" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:58.490" end="3:58.680">こ</span><span begin="3:58.680" end="3:58.860">こ</span><span begin="3:58.860" end="3:59.030">に</span><span begin="3:59.030" end="3:59.550">あ</span><span begin="3:59.550" end="3:59.710">る</span><span begin="3:59.710" end="4:00.260">け</span><span begin="4:00.260" end="4:00.410">れ</span><span begin="4:00.410" end="4:01.150">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">明明都真实存在于此</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">明明都真實存在於此</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Are right here but</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">여기에 있지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sont bien présentes ici</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Están aquí pero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sind zwar hier vorhanden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Estão aqui mas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Они здесь но</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sono qui ma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koko ni aru keredo</span></p><p begin="4:01.400" end="4:06.510" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:01.400" end="4:01.630">そ</span><span begin="4:01.630" end="4:01.780">れ</span><span begin="4:01.780" end="4:02.250">が</span><span begin="4:02.250" end="4:02.850">全</span><span begin="4:02.850" end="4:03.160">て</span><span begin="4:03.160" end="4:03.620">じゃ</span><span begin="4:03.730" end="4:03.920">な</span><span begin="4:03.920" end="4:04.390">い</span><span begin="4:04.390" end="4:04.580">の</span><span begin="4:04.580" end="4:06.510">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">但那绝非全部的真相哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">但那絕非全部的真相哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That is not everything</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그것이 전부는 아니야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce n&apos;est pas tout tu sais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Eso no lo es todo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Doch das ist noch lange nicht alles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Isso não é tudo sabe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это еще не все</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non sono tutto sai</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore ga subete ja nai no yo</span></p><p begin="4:06.990" end="4:09.640" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:06.990" end="4:07.390">君</span><span begin="4:07.390" end="4:07.860">も</span><span begin="4:07.860" end="4:08.090">そ</span><span begin="4:08.090" end="4:08.560">う</span><span begin="4:08.560" end="4:08.760">し</span><span begin="4:08.760" end="4:09.640">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">倘若你也能如此</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">倘若你也能如此</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If you also do the same</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너도 그렇게 해서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si tu me regardais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si tú también haces lo mismo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn auch du auf diese Weise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se você também fizer o mesmo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И если ты тоже вот так</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E se anche tu in questo modo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi mo sou shite</span></p><p begin="4:09.670" end="4:12.330" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:09.670" end="4:09.970">僕</span><span begin="4:09.970" end="4:10.170">を</span><span begin="4:10.170" end="4:10.690">視</span><span begin="4:10.690" end="4:10.870">た</span><span begin="4:10.870" end="4:11.390">の</span><span begin="4:11.390" end="4:11.560">な</span><span begin="4:11.560" end="4:12.330">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">来凝视我的话</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">來凝視我的話</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">And look at me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나를 보았다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">De la même manière</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y me observas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mich betrachten würdest</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E me ver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Посмотришь на меня</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi guardassi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku o mita no nara</span></p><p begin="4:12.570" end="4:18.660" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:12.570" end="4:12.930">白</span><span begin="4:12.930" end="4:13.680">情</span><span begin="4:13.680" end="4:13.880">に</span><span begin="4:14.170" end="4:14.880">映</span><span begin="4:14.880" end="4:15.060">る</span><span begin="4:15.060" end="4:15.560">の</span><span begin="4:15.560" end="4:15.780">か</span><span begin="4:15.780" end="4:18.660">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">会映照出这无尽的白情吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">會映照出這無盡的白情嗎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Will I be reflected as white emotion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">백정으로 비칠까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Serais-je reflétée en une émotion blanche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me reflejaré en esa emoción blanca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Würde ich wohl im weißen Gefühl erscheinen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Será que vou refletir na emoção branca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Отражусь ли я белым чувством</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sarei riflessa come una candida emozione</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hakujou ni utsuru no kana</span></p></div></body></tt>